      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/95142c2955e1896817dc3d6ff9639ac5_5962377137723286969.png",
                "id": "talent12281",
                "key": "The Classics of Acupuncture",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The Classics of Acupuncture"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Gossamer Sprite</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/02943d17a2ad29f325fdac70651d2bae_7861713004591275268.png",
                "id": "talent22678",
                "key": "Universal Diagnosis",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Universal Diagnosis"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pulsing Clarity</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seamless Shield</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pulsing Clarity</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When Action Phase begins:</span> Create <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seamless Shield</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span><br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Seamless Shield</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span></p><p>Provides <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1 Shield</span>, protecting your active character.</p><p>When this effect is removed, or generated again: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, and heal your active character for 1 HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/ed10b8e3def17c518055b3421bfcb94a_1312015481071514985.png",
                "id": "talent27891",
                "key": "Holistic Revivification",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Holistic Revivification"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, heal your active character for 1 HP.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8020649802157262954.png",
                "id": "talent61142",
                "key": "Gossamer Sprite",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/16/35428890/a3d29e698acee488ea48e7cd36af0835_5608192256990469368.png",
                "title": "Gossamer Sprite"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_6199165761605626548.png",
                "id": "talent86989",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/05/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7740210155260419576.png",
                "id": "talent41176",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
